[src:fzf/fzf-examples-p02] ...And a nicer looking alternative, using fzfmenu.
[src:fzf/fzf-examples-p02] If you have `sqlite` installed - you can use it to query DB directly (which takes about ~2ms compared to buku's ~100ms).
